Package core.exceptions

package core.exceptions
  • Exceptions
    Class
    Description
    NoActionRegistered
    Checked exception indicating that no action is registered for a specified ID.
    NoInvokerAvailable
    Checked exception indicating that there is no available invoker for a particular operation.
    NoPolicyManagerRegistered
    Checked exception indicating that no policy manager is registered for a particular operation.
    NoResultAvailable
    Checked exception indicating that no result is available for a specific operation or query in the context of the Cache class.
    OperationNotValid
    Checked exception indicating that an operation is not valid due to a null value, when trying to add a value to a set that already contains said value or when trying to delete a value from a set that doesn't contain said value.
